29954.title: Avatar: The Last Airbender
29954.description: The kids battle Long Feng the Dai Li when they attempt to show the Earth King the vast conspiracy taking place in his city. Zuko becomes seriously ill and has feverish dreams as he faces a spiritual crisis.

29955.title: Avatar: The Last Airbender
29955.description: Aang starts to learn control of the Avatar State from Guru Pathik at the Eastern Air Temple. Sokka is reunited with his father. Toph teaches herself "Metalbending" while Xin Fu and Master Yu are transporting Toph back to her parents. Katara and the generals plan the invasion of the Fire Nation. Later, she sees Zuko and Iroh running their tea shop.

29956.title: SpongeBob SquarePants
29956.description: Plankton hires Patrick to create advertising slogans for the Chum Bucket. // SpongeBob helps Plankton find the perfect anniversary gift for Karen.

29957.title: SpongeBob SquarePants
29957.description: Squidward gets stuck indoors with SpongeBob and Patrick during a storm. // Plankton creates an underground restaurant that threatens to put the Krusty Krab out of business.

29958.title: Teenage Mutant Ninja Turtles
29958.description: Feeling left out of the action, April insists on joining the Turtles on a mission to TCRI, where they learn a shocking secret about April's past.

29959.title: Teenage Mutant Ninja Turtles
29959.description: After encountering mutants and ninjas, Casey Jones decides to take on "pure evil" alone. When he meets Raphael, the two hot-headed fighters must put their dislike for each other aside and work together against a common foe.

29960.title: Kung Fu Panda: Legends of Awesomeness
29960.description: Shifu's evil ex-girlfriend Mei Ling is back...and back together with Shifu! Dubious Po must find out if she is on the level or just using Shifu for her own criminal gain.

29961.title: Kung Fu Panda: Legends of Awesomeness
29961.description: Po and Monkey discover a small village and meet an impostor claiming to be the Dragon Warrior. Po is determined to expose the fraud but could end up doing more harm than good.

29962.title: The Penguins of Madagascar
29962.description: The penguins accidentally launch Leonard the Koala out of the zoo and into midtown Manhattan. // When all the little mammals in the zoo start to disappear the penguins suspect the new boa constrictor, Salvio, who just moved in to the Central Park Zoo.

29963.title: The Penguins of Madagascar
29963.description: The penguins discover the abuse that Randy the sheep gets in the children's zoo from all the children with sticky hands tugging at his wool, and decide to find him a new home. // The duckling Eggy is back. The training that the penguins gave him worked.

29964.title: SpongeBob SquarePants
29964.description: Mr. Krabs makes a wish that he could talk to money. When his wish is magically granted, Krabs learns (to his horror) what all of his dollars, pennies and quarters have been longing for: they want Krabs to spend them. // Squidward trains SpongeBob for the Bikini Bottom dance contest.

29965.title: SpongeBob SquarePants
29965.description: SpongeBob becomes the latest local obsession after a notable food critic gives him high ratings. Now Mr. Krabs is looking to cash in on the fad by making everything in the Krusty Krab Sponge-themed. // SpongeBob helps Patrick get his song some air time at the local radio station.

29966.title: SpongeBob SquarePants
29966.description: SpongeBob and Patrick try to help Sandy rid her Tree Dome of fleas. // When Patrick accidentally takes SpongeBob’s donut he is wracked with guilt over his heinous crime. // SpongeBob battles a persistent speck of food that is on a plate.

29967.title: SpongeBob SquarePants
29967.description: SpongeBob and Patrick fall into a cavern where frightful Trenchbillies keep them hostage. // Squidward's complaints trigger a volcanic eruption.

29968.title: Nella The Princess Knight
29968.description: The kingdom is taken over by sleepy dragons who have been forced out of their home by a monster. // Nella's wild friend Minatori wants to play hide and seek, but she is unwilling to follow Nella's House Rules.

29969.title: Nella The Princess Knight
29969.description: A dragon is scaring the kingdom, and Nella sets off to stop her - only to discover that the dragon has just been trying to make friends. // When troublesome impkins storm the ice cream parlor, it's up to Nella to save the day.

29970.title: Bubble Guppies
29970.description: Blast off with the Bubble Guppies - it's time to learn all about the solar system! Help them begin to learn about outer space in this far-out episode.

29971.title: Bubble Guppies
29971.description: Pack a suitcase and hurry to the airport! Help the Bubble Guppies fly an airplane through the sky and over the clouds - just be sure to keep an eye out for airplane pirates!

29972.title: Dora the Explorer
29972.description: It's Mother's Day, and Dora wants to help Papi bake Mamá a special cake. But three key ingredients are missing: bananas, nuts and chocolate.

29973.title: Dora the Explorer
29973.description: Go-go-go-golden Explorers! Dora and her friends have formed a soccer team and are playing the big Dinosaurs. Can Dora kick the ball into the net and score a goal?

29974.title: Rusty Rivets
29974.description: The comic book action figures Rusty created for Liam come alive and behave just like their conquering characters. // Sammy and Rusty must get back to town before the yummy flower they picked for Sammy's sorbet turns yucky.

29975.title: Rusty Rivets
29975.description: While helping Chef Betty and Sammy compete for the Peachy Keen tasting contest, Rusty and Ruby must find a way to get them working together. // Ruby tries to help the monkeys at the Animal Park come up with some new performances.

29976.title: Blaze And The Monster Machines
29976.description: Crusher and Pickle challenge Blaze and his friends to a sailboat race. But when he tries to cheat, Crusher accidentally crashes both ships onto a tropical island! Blaze and his crew must find the missing pieces of their ship so they can sail home.

29977.title: Blaze And The Monster Machines
29977.description: It’s the day of the Team Truck Challenge, a race where all the trucks get to compete in teams of two! But when Crusher chooses a new partner instead of Pickle, his disappointed sidekick teams up with Blaze to prove his mettle.

29978.title: PAW Patrol
29978.description: Mayor Goodway and Alex take a rowboat out into the bay to get a closer look at a baby whale. A storm is approaching though and the rowboat drifts out of control towards the sea. It's up to the PAW Patrol to rescue them! // While out on a hike Ryder discovers Garby the goat stuck on a cliff edge! He attempts to rescue Garby but gets stranded in the process. He calls the pups for help but drops his Pup Pad down the cliff side!

29979.title: PAW Patrol
29979.description: It’s Adventure Bay Race Day and the pups are about to race each other all across the town to see who is the fastest pup. One other competitor unexpectedly shows up though, Alex in his super trike! // Mr.Porter enters a cake competition and needs Ryder and the pups to help him bake the biggest and tastiest cake. The race is on to get their cake baked and to the competition on time!

29980.title: PAW Patrol
29980.description: Cap'n Turbot accidentally stumbles into a secret cavern that was once a pirate's hideout. When the PAW Patrol rescues him, they find an incomplete treasure map. The adventure is on to find the sunken pirate treasure!

29981.title: SpongeBob SquarePants
29981.description: Pat has a box and he won't show SpongeBob what's inside of it because it's a secret. SpongeBob can't believe Pat would keep something from him and he pretends not to care what's inside, but secretly it's driving him crazy. // Squidward's old High School rival comes to town and brags to Squid about his famous marching band. Feeling outdone, Squid lies and says he has a band, too.

29982.title: SpongeBob SquarePants
29982.description: In order to increase profits, Krabs decides that the Krusty Krab will now be open 24 hours a day. He orders SpongeBob and Squidward to work all night - what's known as the Graveyard Shift. // Ms. Puff pays a visit to the Krusty Krab and Mr. Krabs is instantly smitten with her. He recruits SpongeBob to help him woo Ms. Puff. SpongeBob tries to play match maker, but he screws it all up and Krabs threatens his job!

29983.title: SpongeBob SquarePants
29983.description: Spongebob has an assignment for boating school. He must write an 800 word essay before the next morning. Spongebob starts to write it, but he gets distracted easily and can't keep his mind on his work. // When Patrick's parents come over for Starfish Day, Patrick gets upset that they still think he isn't very smart. Spongebob offers to act stupid next to Pat in front of Patricks' parents in order to make Pat look smarter.

29984.title: The Penguins of Madagascar
29984.description: Marlene plans a game night to help the zoo animals bond but it takes a terrible turn when the snacks run out. While Kowalski, Maurice, and Mort go on a snack run the gaming animals begin to fight over the games - cheating, sore losing, unwilling participation… chaos! The snack runners get trapped by the law at the store, and the zoo animals have to reconcile quickly in order to pull off a risky rescue. This isn’t the kind of bonding Marlene had in mind! // Elmer the dog wants a friend, and thinks he found one in Mort. The penguins are compelled to rescue him, but Elmer doesn’t want to give the little lemur up! Max the cat is recruited to help, and Max uses his dog expertise to lead the boys to the giant dog. Mort is rescued, but at what cost? The penguins think Max has met his slobbery doom in the jaws of the giant mastiff.

29985.title: The Penguins of Madagascar
29985.description: Kowalski's invention that stops time falls into the worst hands possible. King Julien's. The lemur promptly breaks it trapping the two of them in a world frozen in time. Instead of being a disaster, however, they realize they can do everything their hearts desire - invent like crazy, perform on Broadway, play tennis in the middle of the street. But even an infinite playland like this can't last forever! // Special Agent Buck Rockgut makes a "triumphant" return. While hunting the Red Squirrel across the globe, the crusty old bird contacts the penguins with a warning that the diabolical squirrel has a brainwashed sleeper agent among them. They battle each other to a standstill to uncover the agent - will it tear the unit apart? Can trust ever be restored? They have to take a trip to a faraway borough to uncover the truth.

29986.title: Kung Fu Panda: Legends of Awesomeness
29986.description: Self-conscious about his size, Mantis ingests a growth potion that makes him huge. Mantis is initially thrilled with the results, but soon his large size puts the entire village and his friends in grave danger.

29987.title: Kung Fu Panda: Legends of Awesomeness
29987.description: With Po and the Furious Five at each other's throats, Shifu takes them all on a disastrous road trip.

29988.title: Teenage Mutant Ninja Turtles
29988.description: When the Turtles get word of the Kraang's return, they realize there is an even bigger threat coming to Earth!

29989.title: Teenage Mutant Ninja Turtles
29989.description: When the Turtles get word of the Kraang's return, they realize there is an even bigger threat coming to Earth!

29990.title: SpongeBob SquarePants
29990.description: When a storm sweeps the Krusty Krab away, its crew and customers will need a crazed Krabs to lead them back home. // Patrick’s last baby tooth needs to come out, but he’s afraid to let it go.

29991.title: SpongeBob SquarePants
29991.description: SpongeBob and Patrick get hooked on the latest fad - flying your own brain like a tiny drone! // When SpongeBob & Patrick play Mermaidman and Barnacleboy, it's all fun and games until their sworn enemies arrive!

29992.title: SpongeBob SquarePants
29992.description: When SpongeBob thinks he's allergic to his pineapple, Squidward offers to help find him a new home. // Squidward is getting a nose job at the local hospital, and SpongeBob tags along as moral support.

29993.title: Kung Fu Panda: Legends of Awesomeness
29993.description: When Po throws a party and invites the First Furious Five to attend, everyone is shocked to learn that Shifu may not be the courageous hero that they thought he was.

29994.title: Kung Fu Panda: Legends of Awesomeness
29994.description: After Bian Zao steals magical lightning powers, he snubs his villain father Taotie and instead teams up with the vicious Tong Fo and the Croc Bandits. Will Po and Taotie knock some sense into Bian Zao before he uses his powers to destroy the village?

29995.title: The Penguins of Madagascar
29995.description: The penguins are on a mission to fulfill wishes. Private tells Mort that if he throws a penny in the fountain his wish will come true. // King Julien has just discovered April Fools Day. Making up for lost time, he terrorizes the zoo with pranks.

29996.title: The Penguins of Madagascar
29996.description: The toy manufacturer of Rico's doll-girlfriend has upgraded their doll line with a voice chip. // When the penguins are photographed while in action and placed on the new zoo poster they have to stop the presses before the poster gets out to the public.

29997.title: Teenage Mutant Ninja Turtles
29997.description: A fungus mutant spreading through the sewers causes the Turtles and April to experience their worst fears as Leonardo must face his greatest fear- losing his team.

29998.title: Teenage Mutant Ninja Turtles
29998.description: When Donnie upgrades Metalhead's artificial intelligence, he must decide if he can trust a sentient Metalhead or if he has created a new foe.

29999.title: SpongeBob SquarePants
29999.description: When his pet amoeba Spot has puppies, Plankton decides to use them in another of his nefarious plots. // Mr. Krabs is too scared to get his physical, but if he doesn't pass, the Krusty Krab will be shut down!

30000.title: SpongeBob SquarePants
30000.description: Plankton poses as a wish-granting genie in his latest scheme to get the secret formula. // Mr. Krabs' new Krabby soup is a hit - until some heat-loving hippies move into the soup vat!

30001.title: SpongeBob SquarePants
30001.description: When Man Ray rents Squidward's house for the weekend, it's up to SpongeBob and Patrick to stop his evil vacation! // Mr. Krabs takes a vacation and makes Larry the Lobster the temporary manager of the Krusty Krab.

30002.title: Kung Fu Panda: Legends of Awesomeness
30002.description: General Tsin is back with a crazy conspiracy theory about alien rice weevils trying to take over the world. When Po learns Tsin is telling the truth, it's up to the Kung Fu Panda to stop the invasion before it's too late.

30003.title: Kung Fu Panda: Legends of Awesomeness
30003.description: After Zeng unhappily quits his job at the Jade Palace, Po cheers up the weepy goose by telling him he could be a kung fu master. Bad idea, Po. Bad idea.

30004.title: The Penguins of Madagascar
30004.description: King Julien observes children chasing each other, calling out "cooties". He deduces that girls pass this wretched "cooties" with a simple touch. // When Rico crashes the Penguins car and rebuilds it himself, it becomes "possessed" and targets Rico.

30005.title: The Penguins of Madagascar
30005.description: The Amarillo Kid confronts the penguins looking for the infamous Mr. Tux. Apparently the two have a score to settle. // Private is ready to move up in rank within the penguin commando unit, or is he? First he'll have to become a First Class Private.

30006.title: Avatar: The Last Airbender
30006.description: When Aang has a vision that Katara is in danger, Aang, Sokka, and Toph all rush back to Ba Sing Se to save her. They meet up with Iroh, who asks their help in saving Zuko who had been captured as well. As Aang and Iroh journey to the prison where Zuko and Katara are held, Toph and Sokka go to save the Earth King, but are captured by Azula. Aang and Katara are fighting Azula when Zuko shows up and helps Azula. They are overwhealmed by Zuko, Azula and the Dai Li. Aang prepares to let go of Katara to save her. Aang meditates as he rises in cosmic energy but is struck by Azula's lightning bolt and falls. The gang escapes Ba Sing Se and Katara revitalizes Aang using the water from the Spirit Oasis in the North Pole.

30007.title: Avatar: The Last Airbender
30007.description: After sustaining serious injuries at the end of season two, Aang awakens to find himself aboard a Fire Nation ship. Meanwhile, Zuko journeys home.

30008.title: SpongeBob SquarePants
30008.description: Patrick leads an enthusiastic stranger on a tour of his favorite places in Bikini Bottom. // SpongeBob is afraid to get off the roof of the Krusty Krab, but he won't let that stop him from living his life!

30009.title: SpongeBob SquarePants
30009.description: A new secret Krabby Patty formula has disastrous results for Bikini Bottom, and only SpongeBob can save the day. // Mr. Krabs and Plankton have to take boating school classes. Thankfully, SpongeBob's there to show them the ropes!

30010.title: SpongeBob SquarePants
30010.description: When his clarinet goes missing, Squidward must become a hardboiled detective to track it down. // Squidward sends SpongeBob and Patrick on an increasingly difficult scavenger hunt to get them out of his hair.

30011.title: Teenage Mutant Ninja Turtles
30011.description: When the Rat King returns, Splinter must overcome his guilt and fear of the Rat King controlling his mind in order to defeat his foe once and for all.

30012.title: Teenage Mutant Ninja Turtles
30012.description: Facing Shredder's deadly new assassin, Leo must decide whether to risk his brother's lives or ask for Splinter's help. Donnie must put aside his rivalry with Casey in order to uncover a new Kraang plot.

30013.title: Kung Fu Panda: Legends of Awesomeness
30013.description: With his childhood bully back in town, Po must learn to face his fear or risk losing his Dragon Warrior mojo and those that are most important to him.

30014.title: Kung Fu Panda: Legends of Awesomeness
30014.description: Tired of Po getting all the credit and acclaim, the Furious Five quit the Jade Palace and strike out on their own.

30015.title: The Penguins of Madagascar
30015.description: Kowalski is near completion with his mind reading device. But where can he find a processor? // The zoo's new badger exhibit has Private terrified. Marlene sets out to calm his panic by introducing him to the new zoo neighbors, Becky and Stacy.

30016.title: The Penguins of Madagascar
30016.description: Due to the high rate of gadget malfunction, Skipper orders Kowalski to cease with the science. But Kowalski can't resist, he must invent. // When a baby's stroller rolls outside the zoo the penguins chase the baby through the streets of New York.

30017.title: The Penguins of Madagascar
30017.description: The penguin's habitat must undergo a serious repair. So Alice calls in Gus, a strong willed contractor. The penguins must stop Gus before he unearths their secret HQ. // When King Julien wishes on the Gimme Gimme Star, he gets more than he asked for.

30018.title: SpongeBob SquarePants
30018.description: SpongeBob's new friend is a giant fluffy hamster. There's one problem, though: no one else can see him! // Patrick wants to be a horse!

30019.title: SpongeBob SquarePants
30019.description: Gary has a pet translation collar, and he's talking up a storm. Everyone loves it... except for Squidward! // When a small clown gets left behind by the circus, SpongeBob takes the hapless harlequin under his wing.

30020.title: SpongeBob SquarePants
30020.description: SpongeBob can't drive, but you don't need a license to operate a self-driving car! // Patrick thinks he's an old man, so it's up to SpongeBob to remind him how much fun being a kid can be!
